title: Episode 29: Week in the Life
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In this episode, three UW-Green Bay psychology students (Annie Jones, Allee Schramm, and Annemarie Schwery) spend a week interviewing other psychology students about why they decided to major in psychology, what their lives are like as psychology majors, and what they plan to do when they graduate.
